00:07:08,111 --> 00:07:09,670
<b>I'll be right back.</b>

65
00:07:09,679 --> 00:07:11,285
<b>No, I'll go.</b>

66
00:07:12,649 --> 00:07:13,795
<b>What?</b>

67
00:07:14,751 --> 00:07:16,755
<b>If she's there, I should be the one to go.</b>

68
00:07:16,953 --> 00:07:18,150
<b>How can you go there...</b>

69
00:07:18,154 --> 00:07:19,625
<b>I'll go, Eun Seop.</b>

70
00:07:20,523 --> 00:07:22,695
<b>I think she and I need to talk.</b>

71
00:07:22,759 --> 00:07:24,005
<b>I'll be back.</b>

72
