<b>What?</b>

73
00:09:05,361 --> 00:09:08,335
<b>Are you disappointed that I came instead of Eun Seop?</b>

74
00:09:13,870 --> 00:09:16,745
<b>It's not like you fell all the way down. You could've...</b>

75
00:09:17,440 --> 00:09:19,845
<b>climbed down on your own,</b>

76
00:09:21,244 --> 00:09:24,825
<b>just like I made it up here on my own without any difficulty.</b>

77
00:09:33,590 --> 00:09:35,850
<b>- Take it easy. - Bye.</b>

78
00:09:35,858 --> 00:09:37,365
<b>You're right.</b>

79
00:09:39,095 --> 00:09:41,290
<b>I'm disappointed that Eun Seop didn't come.</b>

80
00:09:41,297 --> 00:09:44,845
<b>(Lim Eun Seop)</b>

81
