<b>(Chowon Big Education)</b>

82
00:10:38,354 --> 00:10:40,835
<b>I thought this was my last chance.</b>

83
00:10:47,897 --> 00:10:49,390
<b>If you text me your address, I'll send it to...</b>

84
00:10:49,399 --> 00:10:50,645
