85
00:10:52,135 --> 00:10:54,975
<b>I'd love to come and have a look before buying it.</b>

86
00:10:57,106 --> 00:10:59,145
<b>- Hello. - Hello.</b>

87
00:11:03,479 --> 00:11:05,085
<b>These are so pretty.</b>

88
00:11:05,548 --> 00:11:08,080
<b>What is the symbolic meaning of tulips?</b>

89
00:11:08,084 --> 00:11:10,965
<b>Oh, it's "confession of love."</b>

90
00:11:14,357 --> 00:11:16,365
<b>Would you like some?</b>

91
00:11:25,968 --> 00:11:28,015
<b>My one last chance.</b>

92
00:11:41,150 --> 00:11:44,625
<b>You have no idea how much effort I've made to date.</b>

93
00:11:44,854 --> 00:11:47,435
<b>A couple goes on a trip after they break up.</b>

94
00:11:48,391 --> 00:11:50,720
<b>While they were still together,</b>

95
00:11:50,727 --> 00:11:53,875
<b>they saved up some money to go on a trip together someday.</b>

96
00:11:53,930 --> 00:11:56,890
<b>They go on a trip after they break up? Together?</b>

97
00:11:56,899 --> 00:11:58,460
<b>No, separately.</b>

98
00:11:58,468 --> 00:11:59,760
<b>Really?</b>

99
00:11:59,769 --> 00:12:02,645
<b>And then? What happens?</b>

100
00:12:03,639 --> 00:12:07,755
<b>I did my very best.</b>

101
00:12:13,049 --> 00:12:15,055
<b>But why now?</b>

102
00:12:15,518 --> 00:12:18,480
<b>You never acted on it, so why now? Why this way?</b>

103
00:12:18,488 --> 00:12:20,865
<b>Because I couldn't win his heart no matter how hard I tried.</b>

104
00:12:23,092 --> 00:12:27,065
<b>I just couldn't make it happen. What was I supposed to do?</b>

105
00:12:27,330 --> 00:12:28,575
<b>You see,</b>

106
00:12:30,199 --> 00:12:32,505
<b>I actually had a crush on you.</b>

107
00:12:34,337 --> 00:12:35,515
<b>What?</b>

108
00:12:36,839 --> 00:12:38,945
<b>For a very long time.</b>

109
00:12:41,511 --> 00:12:42,815
<b>I didn't know.</b>

110
00:12:44,380 --> 00:12:46,455
<b>What if you knew, Eun Seop?</b>

111
00:12:51,687 --> 00:12:53,265
<b>Nothing...</b>

112
00:12:54,857 --> 00:12:56,895
<b>would've changed.</b>

113
00:13:01,998 --> 00:13:04,330
<b>- Hey. - I didn't get into any colleges.</b>

114
00:13:04,333 --> 00:13:06,845
<b>- Gosh. - You can try again next year.</b>

115
00:13:14,310 --> 00:13:16,870
<b>- Hey. - Do you want to do this with me?</b>

116
00:13:16,879 --> 00:13:18,185
<b>Hey, Eun Seop!</b>

117
00:13:18,481 --> 00:13:19,980
<b>- Hey, come on. - No.</b>

118
00:13:19,982 --> 00:13:22,580
<b>You can have this. I got too many. Come, I'll buy you jjajangmyeon.</b>

119
00:13:22,585 --> 00:13:25,350
<b>Come on. Everyone's waiting. Hurry.</b>

120
00:13:25,354 --> 00:13:27,365
<b>Hey, come on. Quick.</b>

121
00:13:28,558 --> 00:13:30,765
<b>- Right? - Oh, gosh!</b>

122
00:13:32,929 --> 00:13:35,335
<b>Sure, I may have had many chances, but so what?</b>

123
00:13:37,967 --> 00:13:40,715
<b>The timing was always off.</b>

124
00:13:44,540 --> 00:13:47,455
<b>As if I shouldn't exist in his life.</b>

125
00:14:09,498 --> 00:14:12,805
<b>Eun Seop! Lim Eun Seop!</b>

126
00:14:12,869 --> 00:14:15,100
<b>You said you'd buy me a gaming console with your savings.</b>

127
00:14:15,104 --> 00:14:17,240
<b>- Did you bring it? - Yes, it's in my backpack.</b>

128
00:14:17,240 --> 00:14:19,100
<b>Oh, nice!</b>

129
00:14:19,108 --> 00:14:20,500
<b>Girls, say hi. This is my brother.</b>

130
00:14:20,509 --> 00:14:22,370
<b>- Hello. - He'll buy us jjajangmyeon.</b>

131
00:14:22,378 --> 00:14:23,840
<b>Bye! Let's go.</b>

132
00:14:23,846 --> 00:14:25,585
<b>- I'll call you. - See you later.</b>

133
00:14:25,748 --> 00:14:27,995
<b>Come on. Let's go!</b>

134
00:14:42,398 --> 00:14:44,545
<b>(Good Night Bookstore)</b>

135
00:14:47,069 --> 00:14:50,430
<b>Oh, right. I heard that hobo runs this bookstore now.</b>

136
00:14:50,439 --> 00:14:53,470
<b>- "Hobo"? - That guy, you know.</b>

137
00:14:53,476 --> 00:14:55,355
<b>The one who used to live in the mountains.</b>

138
00:14:58,981 --> 00:15:00,880
<b>All right, let's go!</b>

139
00:15:00,883 --> 00:15:02,155
<b>Okay.</b>

140
00:15:09,125 --> 00:15:11,360
<b>Son, what do you feel like eating?</b>

141
00:15:11,360 --> 00:15:15,575
<b>Well, something with meat?</b>

142
00:15:24,707 --> 00:15:27,115
<b>That's why I couldn't do anything.</b>

143
00:15:29,679 --> 00:15:30,925
<b>I couldn't talk to him...</b>

144
00:15:31,447 --> 00:15:33,585
<b>or even call him once.</b>

145
00:15:37,887 --> 00:15:40,195
<b>But I suddenly became brave...</b>

146
00:15:41,490 --> 00:15:43,095
<b>after you came.</b>

147
00:15:44,660 --> 00:15:45,865
<b>What?</b>

148
00:15:46,095 --> 00:15:47,975
<b>After you came here,</b>

149
00:15:48,431 --> 00:15:51,545
<b>I suddenly became anxious and determined.</b>

150
00:15:51,867 --> 00:15:55,075
<b>I wanted to get in your way and be mean to you.</b>

151
00:15:55,871 --> 00:15:57,245
<b>What did you say?</b>

152
00:15:58,541 --> 00:16:00,245
<b>Be honest.</b>

153
00:16:01,110 --> 00:16:03,715
<b>There was a time when you intentionally got in my way.</b>

154
00:16:40,616 --> 00:16:43,355
<b>Hey, Bo Yeong!</b>

155
00:16:44,520 --> 00:16:47,425
<b>Hey, why are you crying?</b>

156
00:16:47,456 --> 00:16:49,350
<b>Why are you crying? Did something happen?</b>

157
00:16:49,358 --> 00:16:53,005
<b>Because of what happened in the AV room earlier, right?</b>

158
00:16:54,030 --> 00:16:56,335
<b>Mok Hae Won made a move on Lim Eun Seop, didn't she?</b>

159
00:16:57,199 --> 00:17:00,660
<b>Gosh, I never liked that girl.</b>

160
00:17:00,669 --> 00:17:02,830
<b>That sneaky girl.</b>

161
00:17:02,838 --> 00:17:05,145
<b>Gosh, how dare she?</b>

162
00:17:06,609 --> 00:17:07,955
<b>No, never.</b>

163
00:17:08,911 --> 00:17:11,640
<b>- What? - I never got in your way.</b>

164
00:17:11,647 --> 00:17:13,225
<b>Not even once.</b>

165
00:17:14,450 --> 00:17:17,155
<b>You never made a move on him deliberately,</b>

166
00:17:17,219 --> 00:17:19,780
<b>knowing that I had a crush on him?</b>

167
00:17:19,789 --> 00:17:21,295
<b>No, never.</b>

168
00:17:22,258 --> 00:17:24,960
<b>I speculated that you probably liked him,</b>

169
00:17:24,960 --> 00:17:27,535
<b>but I didn't know that Eun Seop was your crush.</b>

170
00:17:28,297 --> 00:17:30,075
<b>You know what?</b>

171
00:17:31,467 --> 00:17:33,575
<b>I have a crush on someone.</b>

172
00:17:34,136 --> 00:17:36,945
<b>I like him so much!</b>

173
00:17:39,275 --> 00:17:40,585
<b>Never.</b>

174
00:17:45,047 --> 00:17:47,825
<b>That's why I can't understand you at all.</b>

175
00:17:48,417 --> 00:17:51,525
<b>Why would you become so mean because of me?</b>

176
00:17:54,356 --> 00:17:55,535
<b>Bo Yeong.</b>

177
00:17:57,126 --> 00:18:00,465
<b>What made you so twisted?</b>

178
00:18:14,877 --> 00:18:16,015
<b>Yes.</b>

179
00:18:17,179 --> 00:18:18,485
<b>I found her.</b>

180
00:18:19,849 --> 00:18:22,725
<b>No, don't worry. I'll bring her down.</b>

181
00:18:23,285 --> 00:18:24,425
<b>Okay.</b>

182
00:18:30,960 --> 00:18:32,865
<b>Follow me, and don't fall behind.</b>

183
00:19:07,830 --> 00:19:09,160
<b>Out of the way.</b>

184
00:19:09,165 --> 00:19:11,475
<b>Move out of the way, everyone!</b>

185
00:19:20,376 --> 00:19:21,515
<b>What?</b>

186
00:19:22,411 --> 00:19:23,670
<b>Do you need anything?</b>

187
00:19:23,679 --> 00:19:25,540
<b>Just tell me the terms of the deal.</b>

188
00:19:25,548 --> 00:19:28,855
<b>Oh, right. I was supposed to tell you that.</b>

189
00:19:37,593 --> 00:19:39,420
<b>What? You don't like it?</b>

190
00:19:39,428 --> 00:19:42,090
<b>- No. - Then you don't have to come.</b>

191
00:19:42,097 --> 00:19:44,745
<b>Who cares about book clubs anyway?</b>

192
00:19:48,604 --> 00:19:49,745
<b>Fine.</b>

193
00:20:17,566 --> 00:20:18,845
<b>You're early.</b>

194
00:20:23,505 --> 00:20:24,815
<b>Thank you.</b>

195
00:20:31,347 --> 00:20:34,825
<b>I hear you're seeing Shim Myeong Yeo these days.</b>

196
00:20:35,517 --> 00:20:36,655
<b>Yes.</b>

197
00:20:39,488 --> 00:20:42,195
<b>And she's holed up in the woods somewhere in Gangwon Province?</b>

198
00:20:46,328 --> 00:20:50,935
<b>You know, I want you to focus on me...</b>

199
00:20:51,500 --> 00:20:53,405
<b>whether it's as a writer...</b>

200
00:20:54,270 --> 00:20:55,375
<b>or as a woman.</b>

201
00:20:56,905 --> 00:20:59,815
<b>- What? - I want you to stop seeing her.</b>

202
00:21:00,676 --> 00:21:03,215
<b>I'm not telling you not to publish her book.</b>

203
00:21:03,579 --> 00:21:05,380
<b>Her book will be published...</b>

204
00:21:05,381 --> 00:21:07,385
<b>whether you see her or not.</b>

205
00:21:07,683 --> 00:21:09,580
<b>So just publish her book...</b>

206
00:21:09,585 --> 00:21:11,295
<b>without seeing her.</b>

207
00:21:11,687 --> 00:21:14,435
<b>Okay? Can you do that?</b>

208
00:21:16,825 --> 00:21:19,035
<b>It's all true, Yun Taek.</b>

209
00:21:21,864 --> 00:21:24,300
<b>- Can I get some water, please? - Coming up.</b>

210
00:21:24,300 --> 00:21:25,545
<b>What do you mean?</b>

211
00:21:25,934 --> 00:21:28,545
<b>And they say I'm the next Shim Myeong Yeo?</b>

212
00:21:29,238 --> 00:21:30,745
<b>Unbelievable.</b>

213
00:21:30,839 --> 00:21:32,800
<b>What does she have that I don't?</b>

214
00:21:32,808 --> 00:21:35,270
<b>Is my writing not as good as hers?</b>

215
00:21:35,277 --> 00:21:36,570
<b>Am I not as good-looking as she is?</b>

216
00:21:36,578 --> 00:21:39,585
<b>Fine, she was born earlier, I'll give her that.</b>

217
00:21:40,883 --> 00:21:42,925
<b>Have you even heard the rumors?</b>

218
00:21:44,353 --> 00:21:45,495
<b>You haven't?</b>

219
00:21:45,788 --> 00:21:47,890
<b>At the peak of her career,</b>

220
00:21:47,890 --> 00:21:50,535
<b>she suddenly quit writing and went back to her hometown.</b>

221
00:21:51,760 --> 00:21:53,320
<b>What did they say?</b>

222
00:21:53,329 --> 00:21:55,790
<b>Everything people say about me is true.</b>

223
00:21:55,798 --> 00:21:56,935
<b>Right.</b>

224
00:21:56,999 --> 00:21:58,405
<b>That's the truth.</b>

225
00:22:00,836 --> 00:22:04,485
<b>They say she had a fling with her brother-in-law,</b>

226
00:22:05,240 --> 00:22:08,655
<b>and that's why her sister killed her husband.</b>

227
00:22:11,146 --> 00:22:12,685
<b>Believe what they say.</b>

228
00:22:17,486 --> 00:22:19,295
<b>So you didn't know?</b>

229
00:22:19,988 --> 00:22:24,395
<b>Then why did you two break up?</b>

230
00:22:24,660 --> 00:22:25,805
<b>Gosh, it's hot.</b>

231
00:22:26,795 --> 00:22:30,275
<b>Excuse me. I asked for water, not broth.</b>

