260
00:26:16,892 --> 00:26:18,035
<b>Yes.</b>

261
00:26:18,360 --> 00:26:21,290
<b>Are you feeling okay?</b>

262
00:26:21,296 --> 00:26:22,760
<b>You didn't catch a cold or anything?</b>

263
00:26:22,764 --> 00:26:24,175
