264
00:26:24,633 --> 00:26:25,875
<b>How are you?</b>

265
00:26:26,001 --> 00:26:27,245
<b>I'm good.</b>

266
00:26:29,504 --> 00:26:32,015
<b>Did you talk to...</b>

267
00:26:32,240 --> 00:26:33,715
