276
00:27:02,337 --> 00:27:03,700
<b>Let me take a short nap.</b>

277
00:27:03,705 --> 00:27:05,100
<b>What short nap?</b>

278
00:27:05,107 --> 00:27:07,200
<b>You slept all this time. Get up already.</b>

279
00:27:07,209 --> 00:27:09,010
<b>I'm bored. Come on.</b>

280
00:27:09,011 --> 00:27:10,215
