288
00:27:26,061 --> 00:27:27,260
<b>I'm going to make you into the Joker.</b>

289
00:27:27,262 --> 00:27:29,075
<b>Okay, I'll get up.</b>

290
00:27:30,232 --> 00:27:33,130
<b>Hey, no! Get up.</b>

291
00:27:33,135 --> 00:27:35,100
<b>You're really not going to get up? Come on.</b>

292
00:27:35,103 --> 00:27:36,975
<b>Hey! Get up.</b>

293
00:27:42,210 --> 00:27:43,355
<b>Oh, boy.</b>

294
00:27:45,080 --> 00:27:46,240
<b>- Hello, Eun Sil. - What?</b>

295
00:27:46,248 --> 00:27:49,295
<b>- What a very casual entrance. - Wasn't it?</b>

296
00:27:49,351 --> 00:27:52,720
<b>Gosh, our timing is finally right for a change.</b>

297
00:27:52,721 --> 00:27:53,925
<b>I know.</b>

298
00:27:55,657 --> 00:27:57,695
<b>Look at those roses.</b>

299
00:27:59,961 --> 00:28:01,930
<b>Hey. Aren't these...</b>

300
00:28:01,930 --> 00:28:04,635
<b>the same ones you gave me a long time ago?</b>

301
00:28:05,000 --> 00:28:06,205
<b>What?</b>

302
00:28:08,336 --> 00:28:09,545
<b>What...</b>

303
00:28:09,971 --> 00:28:12,015
<b>Are you asking me out like this?</b>

304
00:28:12,207 --> 00:28:13,400
<b>Yes.</b>

305
00:28:13,408 --> 00:28:16,310
<b>I'm Lee Jang Woo, the student body president.</b>

306
00:28:16,311 --> 00:28:19,555
<b>- I know that you're Lee Jang Woo. - You know me?</b>

307
00:28:20,182 --> 00:28:21,755
<b>Those roses are white.</b>

308
00:28:21,917 --> 00:28:26,120
<b>You must be very kind and innocent, right?</b>

309
00:28:26,121 --> 00:28:27,325
<b>Yes, I am.</b>

310
00:28:27,889 --> 00:28:29,350
<b>But that's too bad.</b>

311
00:28:29,357 --> 00:28:33,565
<b>Baek Gyeong asked me out during lunch earlier today.</b>

312
00:28:33,829 --> 00:28:35,275
<b>And I said yes.</b>

313
00:28:35,497 --> 00:28:36,635
<b>What?</b>

314
00:28:36,965 --> 00:28:38,205
<b>Sorry.</b>

315
00:28:39,801 --> 00:28:42,415
<b>- I guess our timing didn't match. - Timing?</b>

316
00:28:43,572 --> 00:28:46,515
<b>- What is that? - It's nothing.</b>

317
00:28:46,575 --> 00:28:48,410
<b>- Can I read it? - No, you can't. Why?</b>

318
00:28:48,410 --> 00:28:50,815
<b>Don't take it. Put that back down. Why?</b>

319
00:28:51,179 --> 00:28:53,380
<b>- Thank you. - But that's not for you. Why?</b>

320
00:28:53,381 --> 00:28:55,610
<b>- Put that back down. - But I'll have to say no.</b>

321
00:28:55,617 --> 00:28:57,895
<b>- I said no. - What?</b>

322
00:28:58,320 --> 00:29:00,020
<b>Guys, I said no, okay?</b>

323
00:29:00,021 --> 00:29:02,020
<b>Eun Sil, that letter... Eun Sil, the letter!</b>

324
00:29:02,023 --> 00:29:04,550
<b>- Give me the letter. Eun Sil! - He got rejected.</b>

325
00:29:04,559 --> 00:29:08,260
<b>- He got rejected! - She said no!</b>

326
00:29:08,263 --> 00:29:10,290
<b>When did you guys come?</b>

327
00:29:10,298 --> 00:29:12,660
<b>- She said no. - How embarrassing.</b>

328
00:29:12,667 --> 00:29:15,575
<b>- Where are you going? - He got rejected!</b>

329
00:29:16,838 --> 00:29:18,115
<b>Then...</b>

330
00:29:18,573 --> 00:29:20,700
<b>if you didn't go out with Baek Gyeong back then...</b>

331
00:29:20,709 --> 00:29:22,540
<b>- Of course, I would've said no. - Right?</b>

332
00:29:22,544 --> 00:29:25,880
<b>Yes. You weren't my type back then. Not at all.</b>

333
00:29:25,881 --> 00:29:29,780
<b>I was attracted to bad boys back then.</b>

334
00:29:29,785 --> 00:29:31,150
<b>Bad boys?</b>

335
00:29:31,153 --> 00:29:33,520
<b>I guess Baek Gyeong was kind of bad.</b>

336
00:29:33,522 --> 00:29:35,520
<b>I heard you're going somewhere nice later.</b>

337
00:29:35,524 --> 00:29:37,890
<b>- Somewhere nice? - Yes, I'm going to follow you.</b>

338
00:29:37,893 --> 00:29:39,465
<b>It's going to be fun.</b>

339
00:29:39,661 --> 00:29:41,190
<b>Follow me where?</b>

340
00:29:41,196 --> 00:29:45,705
<b>I've already put in a word, okay?</b>

341
00:29:48,203 --> 00:29:50,275
<b>Eun Sil? Eun Sil.</b>

342
00:29:51,072 --> 00:29:52,840
<b>- Eun Sil. - Hey!</b>

343
00:29:52,841 --> 00:29:54,040
<b>Hi, Ji Young.</b>

344
00:29:54,042 --> 00:29:56,240
<b>- Hello. - Hey, you can have some too.</b>

345
00:29:56,244 --> 00:29:58,580
<b>- It's all right. - Okay.</b>

346
00:29:58,580 --> 00:30:00,610
<b>- I'm here. - Hi, come in.</b>

347
00:30:00,615 --> 00:30:02,880
<b>This radish water kimchi is perfectly ripe and delicious.</b>

348
00:30:02,884 --> 00:30:05,720
<b>- Goodness, that looks good. - Come try some.</b>

349
00:30:05,720 --> 00:30:07,980
<b>- Thank you so much. - Sure.</b>

350
00:30:07,989 --> 00:30:10,990
<b>It's so warm in here. Can you make me some sesame oil?</b>

351
00:30:10,992 --> 00:30:13,290
<b>Okay, I'll make it, so come pick it up tomorrow.</b>

352
00:30:13,295 --> 00:30:14,990
<b>Okay, thanks.</b>

353
00:30:14,996 --> 00:30:17,730
<b>By the way, did you hear?</b>

354
00:30:17,732 --> 00:30:19,260
<b>Hear what?</b>

355
00:30:19,267 --> 00:30:21,770
<b>The daughter of Hodu House came here.</b>

356
00:30:21,770 --> 00:30:24,030
<b>The daughter of that family always lived there.</b>

357
00:30:24,039 --> 00:30:25,600
<b>No, not her.</b>

358
00:30:25,607 --> 00:30:28,015
<b>You know, the daughter...</b>

359
00:30:30,312 --> 00:30:33,255
<b>You know, the daughter who killed her husband.</b>

360
00:30:34,015 --> 00:30:35,550
<b>Can you believe it?</b>

361
00:30:35,550 --> 00:30:38,350
<b>How can she come back here after doing that to her husband?</b>

362
00:30:38,353 --> 00:30:41,420
<b>Well, the women from that family are all so spiteful.</b>

363
00:30:41,423 --> 00:30:43,720
<b>Even their mom was spiteful.</b>

364
00:30:43,725 --> 00:30:46,790
<b>Both her daughters were just like her.</b>

365
00:30:46,795 --> 00:30:50,075
<b>How spiteful could one be to kill her own husband...</b>

366
00:30:51,399 --> 00:30:55,515
<b>Right, weren't you close with her granddaughter?</b>

367
00:30:55,837 --> 00:30:58,270
<b>Bo Yeong, what are you doing? Go to your room.</b>

368
00:30:58,273 --> 00:31:01,855
<b>No, I need to go to the academy. Bye.</b>

369
00:31:15,657 --> 00:31:16,995
<b>You promised me...</b>

370
00:31:17,759 --> 00:31:21,565
<b>not to tell anyone either.</b>

371
00:31:24,699 --> 00:31:26,360
<b>I trusted Joo Hee.</b>

